# SoulStep – Admin Web  (apps/soulstep-admin-web)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to .env.local for local development.  Do not commit .env.local.
# In production (Vercel), set these as Vercel environment variables via
# `vercel env add` or the Vercel dashboard — see PRODUCTION.md.
#
# Legend:
#   [optional]    — has a sensible built-in default; set only to override
#   [conditional] — required only when a related feature is enabled


# ── API Proxy (dev server only) ───────────────────────────────────────────────

# [optional] Catalog API URL used by the Vite dev server to proxy /api requests.
# NOT VITE_-prefixed — this variable is consumed by vite.config.ts at dev-server
# startup and is never exposed to the browser bundle.
#
# Default: http://127.0.0.1:3000  (local catalog API)
#
# Hybrid mode — run the local admin UI against the production catalog API:
# API_PROXY_TARGET=https://catalog-api.soul-step.org
# API_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:3000


# ── Scraper API ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# [optional] Direct URL for the soulstep-scraper-api.
# When set, the admin web calls the scraper API at this URL directly, bypassing
# the catalog proxy at /api/v1/admin/scraper.
# Use for local hybrid mode (local scraper + production catalog API).
# When unset, all scraper calls are routed through the catalog proxy.
# VITE_SCRAPER_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8001


# ── Frontend URL ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# [optional] Public URL of the customer-facing web frontend.
# Used in the SEO detail page to generate place-preview links for review.
# Default: https://soul-step.org
# VITE_FRONTEND_URL=https://soul-step.org

# Sentry error tracking (production only)
# VITE_SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@sentry.io/yyy
